text: Magnus III (1240 - December 18, 1290) was King of Sweden from 1275 until 1290. Not much is known about his early life. It is believed he was born around 1240 in an unknown location. ==Children== One of his children was Birger of Sweden (1280 - May 31, 1321). title: Magnus III of Sweden
